---

This project builds upon several open-source projects:
- Query2Label (https://github.com/ddw2AIGROUP2CQUPT/Query2Labels)
- LabCR (Shi et al., "Label-aware Calibration and Relation-preserving in Visual
  Intention Understanding", TIP 2024)
- Asymmetric Loss (https://github.com/Alibaba-MIIL/ASL)
- Slot Attention (Locatello et al., NeurIPS 2020)
- Janus-Pro (https://github.com/deepseek-ai/Janus)
- Intentonomy (https://github.com/facebookresearch/Intentonomy)

Please respect the licenses of those respective projects.
